{"tid":274102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「混血AV史上第一美」出道了！嬌羞神情擁E奶美胸","createTime":"2017-06-07T05:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T05:51:57.000Z","uid":41351,"like":42,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7dd42d95bbb36cfe79c3b594c092a290759c6b2","tid":274102,"uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:30:49.000Z","msg":"看色情片就是喜歡看見賞心悅目的AV女優，不過最怕的就是看見圖影不符的女主角，或技巧太差的男主角，若出現絕世美女那可是會讓色情片聲名大噪。最近被封為「AV史上第一美人」的混血新人月島杏奈（月島アンナ）打著「零修圖」出道了，嬌羞的神情搭上細緻的肌膚讓人一秒墜入愛河。<br />\n根據《Menclub》網站報導，AV界新人月島杏奈（月島アンナ）即將出道，擁有俄羅斯、美國及日本三國混血基因，五官非常立體、亮眼，肌膚也是吹彈可破，且身高171公分還有E罩杯的姣好身材。<br />\n不過其實他是貨真價實的「男兒身」，在出道的封面上也寫著「ニューハーフ(人妖)」的字眼，就連穿內褲的性感照也用馬賽克打馬。如此這麼楚楚可憐的模樣，再搭配上性感的美胸，實在讓人難以想像他是個男性，這名新人未來也將在AV界掀起一陣旋風。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-06-07/656/20170607002768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-06-07%2F656%2F20170607002768.jpg&h=fba5c42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-06-07/656/20170607002771.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-06-07%2F656%2F20170607002771.jpg&h=f391cb46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20170607002739-260808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20170607002739-260808&d=RqhwnB06MJQCJkBLgkiVqkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0839a93d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20170607002739-260808</a><br />\n竟然是他"},{"pid":"71e59a5e45c436b151446cb94ff29e6d9e1128e5","tid":274102,"uid":121237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d233c79025